         <div xml:id="alalal-j36749"><!-- l4d48a7 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-j36749-Hd1e99">Articulus 7</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36749-d1e101">
               <cb ed="#Bf" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="25"/>ARTICULUS VII. 
<lb ed="#Bf" n="26"/>An in judicio extremo sol et luna 
eclip<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="27"/>sim patientur ? 
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36749-d1e112">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="28"/>Deinde quaeritur de hoc quod dicit, E,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="29"/>paulo post initium: <quote xml:id="alalal-j36749-Qd1e118"> Sol ei luna 
eclip<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="30"/>sim patientur, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36749-d1e124">
               <cb ed="#Bf" n="c"/>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="31"/>Videtur enim hoc impossibile: quia
<lb ed="#Bf" n="32"/>sol et luna numquam possunt simul pati
<lb ed="#Bf" n="33"/>eclipsim : sed sol in conjunctione 
eclip<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="34"/>sim patitur, et luna in oppositione : ergo
<lb ed="#Bf" n="35"/>falsum est quod dicit.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36749-d1e140">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="36"/>Responsio. Ad hoc dicendum, quod
<lb ed="#Bf" n="37"/>Mieronymus multa dicit signa debere
<lb ed="#Bf" n="38"/>praecedere diem judicii, quae quia nescio
<lb ed="#Bf" n="39"/>si vera sunt, ideo non pono. Sed istud
<lb ed="#Bf" n="40"/>videtur dicendum, quod si sol et luna
<pb ed="#Bf" n="662"/>
               <cb ed="#Bf" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="1"/>obscurabuntur simul, sicut videtur velle
<lb ed="#Bf" n="2"/>Hieronymus, hoc non erit per causam
<lb ed="#Bf" n="3"/>naturalem conjunctionis vel 
praventio<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="4"/>nis corum, sed potius virtute divina, ut
<lb ed="#Bf" n="5"/>terror hominibus incutiatur, sicut Lucas
<lb ed="#Bf" n="6"/>innuit, xx1, 25: <quote xml:id="alalal-j36749-Qd1e170"
                      source="http://scta.info/resource/lc21_25@1-7">Et erunt signa in sole,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="7"/>et luna</quote>, etc. Sequitur: <quote xml:id="alalal-j36749-Qd1e175"
                      source="http://scta.info/resource/lc21_25@10-14">Et in terris pres-
<lb ed="#Bf" n="8"/>sura gentium</quote>, etc. 
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36749-d1e182">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="9"/>Vel forte, quia lumine solis et lune
<lb ed="#Bf" n="10"/>cuncta generantur et vivunt: et tunc
<lb ed="#Bf" n="11"/>stabit generatio : ideo etiam defectus 
di<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="12"/>citur esse luminarium.
</p>
         </div>
